Package: StatFlow
Title: Interactive Introductory Data Analysis Platform
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Manuel", "Spínola", 
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr",
           role  = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: A Shiny-based interactive platform for introductory data analysis,
    part of the StatSuite ecosystem. Includes modules for data loading,
    exploration, graphics, comparing means and frequencies, correlation,
    and understanding p-values. Designed for teaching and research in
    ecology and biodiversity sciences.
